Package: wasta-multidesktop-xenial
Architecture: all
Depends: lightdm, wasta-core-xenial, wmctrl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wasta-Linux MultiDesktop
 Ensures cross-desktop compatibility between Cinnamon, Unity, Gnome-Shell,
 and XFCE desktops. A script is executed on login to make necessary
 adjustments based on detected window manager.
